🚨 Re-scheduled🚨

💦🌿 BAKUN WATERFALLS ESCAPADE + BAGUIO SIDETRIP 🌿💦
September 20-21 2025 (Sat–Sun)
Get ready for an epic adventure as we chase the top 3 waterfalls of Bakun, Benguet and cap it off with a refreshing Baguio City sidetrip! 🥾🍓⛰️

✨ Waterfalls to Explore in Bakun:
🌊 Tekip Falls 
🌊 Pattan Falls
🌊 Mangta Falls

📍 Bakun, Benguet + Baguio City
🗓️ September 20-21, 2025 (Sat–Sun)

✅ All-in hassle-free package
✅ 2D1N adventure for joiners and barkadas
✅ Guided hike + city chill vibes in Baguio

📌 INCLUSIONS:
VAN TRANSFER – ENTRANCE FEES – GUIDE FEE – COORDINATOR FEE – BAGTAG  – BAGUIO SIDETRIP

📌 EXCLUSIONS:
❌ Meals (BYOB or buy on-site)
❌ Shower Fee

🚐 Pick-up Points:
– Cavite
– Baclaran
– Buendia
– Mayflower parking
– Centris
– NLEX, SCTEX, and TPLEX exits

Slots are limited! Experience both adventure and chill in one trip. Don’t miss this unforgettable Benguet getaway! 🍃💧

📩 Message us now to reserve your slot!
